Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Located in the growing East Memphis submarket with excellent access to I-240 interstate making Thousand Oaks Business Center only minutes from Downtown Memphis, the Memphis International Airport, the Poplar Corridor, North Memphis, Eastern Arkansas and the TN-385 Corridor.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Three Building Office Center. Each building is four stories. Beautifully landscaped park-like setting with newly remodeled fitness center with men's and women's locker rooms. On-site property management team. Tenant monument signage available
